g\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/b21a922eaaa087abbdecee59b21c18c5.avif?t=1772596081\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rampage of revenge can take its toll on Mr. Peppermint. The crueler his actions, the more twisted the story unfolds and his psyche crumbles. Paradoxes and inconsistencies appear. Unanswered questions manifest. As this once dedicated detective  spirals out of control, question who is really the serial killer…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.poster.avif?t=1772596081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.webm?t=1772596081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287560/extras/201c7bb10c8d65b9ccace06d21938763.mp4?t=1772596081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></p>",
